Title: S6. Ep. 263  Caris Baker: Faith, Art and Being About It.
Description:
Today's guest is Caris Baker; she is memorable for so many reasons. She is a woman of faith, family, and work. As a graduate from Full Sail University, she is a leader in the #game industry and cognized for her accomplishments when Full Sail inducted her into their #HallofFame. Caris recognizes that #gratitude is a value that most people need to practice daily. 

I believe she is a person that everyone would want to have in their corner and as one of the top five people they want as their friend.  I know I do.

Tune in to learn more about Caris and reach out to her on LinkedIn.
